Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:15.64,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby declare the restoration of Japan as a legitimate, independently controlled country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.04,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the group that occupied Fukuoka Base, Sawasaki Atushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:26.17,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,was the Chief Cabinet Secretary of the former Japan during the second term of the Kururugi Administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.39,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,He sought asylum in the Chinese Federation after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:33.30,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,However, we think that he's making use of the internal unrest caused by Zero to carry out this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.55,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,We are now in the midst of investigating whether the Order of the Black Knights has anything to do with this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.42,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The incident at Kaminejima was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.42,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're not related!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.76,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,What did Kyoto say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.24,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... It seems that they didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:46.60,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, including the acquisition of Sakuradite, was done arbitrarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.94,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:29.02,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Sawasaki's group is cooperating with the terrorist cells within the Kyushu Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.85,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\i1}Honshu is the largest of the four main islands that make up Japan, while Shikoku is the smallest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.85,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,After destroying the land traffic network that linked the Honshu block and Shikoku block,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.53,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\i1}Note: Liaodong is a peninsula in northeastern China. In reality, it was one of the areas that China ceded to Japan after the first Sino-Japanese war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.53,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,together with support from the Chinese Federation's Liaodong military district,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:40.51,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\i1}Note: Fukuoka, Nagasaki, and Oita are all provinces on Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:40.51,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,they are using Fukuoka, Nagasaki and Oita as a center of operation to increase the area they have captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.57,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,According to General Tsao from the Chinese Federation, they are only providing humanitarian aid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:50.00,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,and are not going against the Manila Convention...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.08,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,How is Suzaku-kun doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.43,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll definitely obey if we engage in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.54,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.76,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Where is His Highness Schneiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:55.97,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,At the Tokyo settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.74,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing that follows after the problem with Suzaku is this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:04.99,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Although the master is not around, we have to clear this obstacle or we won't be able to counter the Gefjun Disturber...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.99,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I... am not qualified to be your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.85,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about that insubordination incident, {Meirei ihan no koto nara}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:20.48,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Schneiser said that there's no need to take responsibility for it since it took place during an irregular moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.29,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:28.54,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a burden? Making you my knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.41,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm thankful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.22,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.90,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I recalled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:33.67,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I... killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.08,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.49,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But... I wasn't punished at all. I was living freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.76,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'm being protected like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.41,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I, alone... without caring about the martyrs to duty and the Elevens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,590)}I'm not qualified as I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.51,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,"Qualified"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:54.67,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I am also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.00,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness Cornelia, we are taking too much damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.22,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,With this weather, we are unable to make use of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.39,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,As for land-based combat, it's better if we wait for the weather to stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.80,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,It's sure fortunate to have such an intense storm blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.34,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make use of this chance to seize Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.26,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,General Tsao, Heaven is acting as our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.53,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,We will win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.19,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to declare martial law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.70,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,That would just increase the uneasiness among the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.81,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Send a letter to the EU's Foreign Minister Gandolfi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.58,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, also contact the Toromo Institution in Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.44,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness Schneiser, using Toromo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.09,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Prime Minister, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.29,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.20,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.94,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can help out with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.55,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to do something as the Vice Governor-General of Area 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.64,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. That feeling alone is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.49,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.52,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't let the Vice Governor-General do anything." That was the order from the Governor-General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.69,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,From Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.19,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Although I willfully selected my knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.78,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.19,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,I too feel that Kururugi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.62,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, try to be understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.92,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the current situation, not even Cornelia has the time for such things, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:14.39,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Darlton, about what I said earlier, an acquaintance of mine knows a route. I'll try and ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.41,CG ON,Dalton,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.35,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We've already put so much effort into preparing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.52,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the school festival is going to be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.05,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the problem. It's war, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.54,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,War?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.93,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Even though a government in exile is stuck in between,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.61,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,this is war against the Chinese Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:33.64,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.94,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, what about the outdoor booths that we're supposed to borrow from the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.22,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm going to do the paperwork today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:43.07,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want to go to the science department after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.74,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... about {\i1}that{\i0} present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.90,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.87,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.28,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Lloyd said he'd give it to me if I asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.69,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.43,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,That womanizer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.80,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already. Continue your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.46,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you say that, I'm doing the work of three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.07,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku is with the army. Kallen is in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.33,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining idiot has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:10.28,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)}A-Ah... Lelouch, that fellow, seems to have changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.08,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was shocking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.16,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am still in confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.31,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lulu is actually Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:22.17,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}I haven't told anyone about it because I want to meet Lulu and confirm it for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.77,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(316,0)\i1}Did I... write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.82,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I forget about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:32.26,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About Nana-chan's brother... and about Zero...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.05,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Z-01, Float Attachment contacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.46,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming the linkage. The avionics are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.16,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,You're really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.48,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,You got top class in the float simulation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.88,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.07,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you quit being a knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:55.42,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even as I am now... Her Highness, Princess Euphemia will still accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:07:03.34,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,If further problems were to arise, I feel that... she would start to hate herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.61,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A decorative Vice Governor-General...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.78,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still want to put effort into whatever I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.09,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Brother Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.69,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was unable to avenge you even though I met Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.85,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I still can't think of a way to save Lelouch and Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.72,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\i1}I'm not as powerful as Sister or Brother Schneiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.49,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just a burden no matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.64,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I even realize it, I find myself acting willfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.56,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I went against Sister's decision and selected a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.98,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.29,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.80,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to do the paperwork today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.11,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,A royal is inside viewing at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.16,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.45,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... In other words...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.82,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We won't join up with Sawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't independence. It's just a puppet government.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,One controlled by the Chinese Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.63,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,But they are calling themselves "Japan".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a change of name and master. There's no future in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Disregard that "Japan".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.06,CG ON,Shogo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, then you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.35,CG ON,Kosetsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to disregard Britannia's action?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.52,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, I think it's better if you clearly explain the objective of the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.96,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.78,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we leave the Sawasaki's incident out of this, what is our immediate objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To form an independent country in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.94,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Independent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:33.95,CG ON,Shogo,0000,0000,0000,,Country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.02,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.32,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Us? A country...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.70,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You are indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.03,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:45.33,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much the Order of the Black Knights grows...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.38,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is a large country that reigns over a third of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.25,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Doing that with just us is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then I ask you:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:56.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you waiting for to defeat Britannia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.05,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Someone will take your place and do that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.88,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A chance will come someday if you keep on waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:07.06,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If you yourself don't act, that "someday" definitely won't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.72,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.66,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.41,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Case Delta has occurred. Case Delta has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.28,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Taking her in! Seal the roads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.70,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, I just want to thank Princess Euphemia, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.19,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Just one look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.98,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Seal up all the roads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.74,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: Seal up all the roads leading to the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.37,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.25,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,From the hotel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.67,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you... I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.25,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The interrogation room has been prepared. Bring her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.63,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.42,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.22,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The sky has cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.18,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,We can now resume land-based combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.23,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness Schneiser's proposal can be executed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.60,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the Special Envoy can break through?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.82,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Possible if Kururugi is doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.27,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,He really is someone who's difficult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:56.07,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,But due to the absence of a commanding officer, they are depending entirely on technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:59.24,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Missiles incoming. They are launching from Fukuoka Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.32,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,One minute five seconds before impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.16,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from them. The aerial defense is well thought-out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.74,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I clear up the volley of missiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.29,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to handle it from our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.05,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Impact confirmed! We have struck the enemy's floating battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.54,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, even if it's a new model, a single ship is just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.64,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.61,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,We have already confirmed it using the Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:36.11,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Major Kururugi, I'm going through the mission instruction one last time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.33,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Special Envoy is going to use this ship to penetrate the enemy's frontline from a high altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.95,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,We are now heading towards the point where you will take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:48.12,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Guided Weapon Z-01 Lancelot will use the Float Unit to launch an assault against the headquarters of the enemy, Fukuoka Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:52.54,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The energy consumption while floating is high, so please keep track of your operational time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.79,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.72,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,ME booster...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.72,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:22.59,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that a bomber has taken off from the enemy battleship, but its speed is faster than that of a fighter plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.98,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Getting visuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.86,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,A KnightMare...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.29,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,It's not transported by air, but actually in flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.09,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the one in the reports...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.84,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,That miraculous weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.21,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That means inside it is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:47.81,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,The presence of Sawasaki Atushi is the pretext those people are giving for taking over the Kyushu Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.73,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the new Japanese government will collapse if he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:56.61,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese Federation will lose their reason to intervene as well, and will have no choice but to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.96,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That... is the enemy headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.13,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Open channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.11,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:29.22,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is heading here, are you Kururugi's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.60,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He actually has a child like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:39.02,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... Back then when Princess Euphemia saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.26,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.92,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if you were shining brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.11,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.83,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I should have thanked you for lending me your clothes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.32,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.00,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm not that great of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.17,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely useless compared to my elder sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.59,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,You are not useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:03.13,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia being useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:09.40,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good-for-nothing... Completely useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:13.02,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are just commoners...  I'm not pretty at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.84,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. You are really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.69,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.74,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really useless... Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.85,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You hate yourself, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.94,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the same goes for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.66,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I know it clearly in my head... about Suzaku too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.72,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see! Suzaku too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:39.87,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't let Princess Euphemia say that she's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.81,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Because...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.71,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.08,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Because I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.63,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,To me... {I can't get wet without thinking of Princess Euphemia?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.51,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.26,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It was great meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.26,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.39,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I understand it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.85,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I myself wanted to put an end to the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.27,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.78,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to take away the dream of Japan's independence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.79,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, realize that through the correct methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:10.24,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to live on willfully like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.41,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing with that idealistic view of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.58,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.78,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The VARIS is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That is a Ganruu from the Chinese Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:27.34,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,He was distracted by just a conversation. He's still a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.51,CG ON,Scheneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.25,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Schneiser !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.47,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to send a private transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.56,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Filler is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.39,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! The Float System was destroyed as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.23,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use the Avalon to charge straight into the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.28,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.82,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an all-round shield! We'd be shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.91,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, for the moment, use the remaining energy only for combat and communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.67,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender, Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:02.38,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that I will treat you well as the orphaned child of Prime Minister Kururugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.03,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.46,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive myself if I made use of my father's name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.88,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see, aren't you similar to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.93,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That stubbornness of yours is pretty similar to your father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.31,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.98,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.91,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, I... erm... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.48,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Right now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.94,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.30,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.66,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.44,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.81,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's the problem this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.41,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,E-Erm... It's nothing. Just something private.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.33,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I'll fall deeply in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.27,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.79,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku... Your stubbornness... Your gentleness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.60,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Your sad eyes... Your silliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You getting bitten by cats... I like it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.84,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,So don't hate yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.93,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I've made you worried instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.73,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,As a person, you are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.48,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Always so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.72,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you... When you said you were a princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:09.92,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Deciding that I should go to school... Choosing me as a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.11,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You are always...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.02,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm always sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.91,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I suddenly realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:21.75,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But due to that suddenness, I felt as if the door to my heart has become unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.37,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.83,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Stop that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.13,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Can I make one last request of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.21,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,"Last"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.47,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hate yourself no matter what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:39.06,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Also, eliminate everything about me when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:45.65,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cause my friends any trouble, so tell them that I've transferred schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.86,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.44,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,My... energy has been used up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.83,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:55.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Please send my regards to Cecile-san, Lloyd-san, and His Highness Schneiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.56,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I still overestimated myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.15,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.37,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.29,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.87,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:12.97,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.05,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reaction on the radar. Something suddenly appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.77,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.13,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Visuals captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.76,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:29.29,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,That white armor is the one called Lancelot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.79,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Reckless way of fighting as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that he has backup this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A single machine is used to cause confusion in the main base to bring about an irregularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he fails, Cornelia can make her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Schneiser... Is he the one behind this strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.76,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the Hadron Cannon supposed to be incomplete?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.38,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It was finished...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:58.55,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been the one to complete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:03.26,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,We sort of managed to finish it by putting the theory behind the Gefjun Disturber to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.85,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,But the development of the Float System was my loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.40,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my opponent is that pudding Earl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.62,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,This was unintentional cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.57,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... This makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi, is the Lancelot still able to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.78,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, it is indeed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.93,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.21,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,They are speaking on the open channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:24.61,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.95,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,Turn up the volume! We need to confirm his objective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.21,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,An Energy Filler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to attack the enemy's headquarters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.88,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:35.92,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.39,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.85,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish won't be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.52,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I shall engage in this battle before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.37,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Launch all units! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.22,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Zero and Kururugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.96,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, aren't your people comrades of those fighting for the sake of Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:19.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Order of the Black Knights, are the enemy of all those who use violence unreasonably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.23,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,"Unreasonably"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.80,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it for Japan's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:26.06,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sawasaki-san, why did you escape to the Chinese Federation if you are doing it for Japan's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.52,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You should have stayed for the sake of everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.43,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.05,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cooperative operation? Gawain and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.78,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.49,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku and Lelouch are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.33,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What? Zero is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.99,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's with Kururugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:49.66,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What is that man thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.77,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,In order to escape detection by Britannia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:54.83,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,using the Gawain for a sole mission is the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.71,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But it would have been easier if the Guren had been used to provide cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.28,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't head back home or to school anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.16,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, even if we don't cooperate with the Lancelot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.01,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What we need is not victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:12.23,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What is crucial is the fact that the Order of the Black Knights participated in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.94,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this won't be officially reported, but rumors will spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:23.03,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,As Zero said, this is going to aid us in announcing our stance to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.12,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with asking help from foreign countries while waiting for a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.34,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,That is what it means to strategize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.22,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\i1}Note: Kagoshima is located on the southwestern end of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.22,CG ON,Tsao,0000,0000,0000,,There is still a defensive line left in Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.25,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.31,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sawasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.09,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.18,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.92,CG ON,Sawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Taking down the largest fortress in Kyushu... so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:21:00.19,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,About the terrorist incident that broke out in the Kyushu block due to an anti-government organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.32,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,under the lightning-quick operation carried out by Governor-General Cornelia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:06.63,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Sawasaki Atushi and four other old Japanese government members were detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:10.09,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,More than half of the soldiers from the Chinese Federation Army that took part in this incident were detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.37,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, the governing body of the Chinese Federation has announced that this incident
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:18.21,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,is a unilateral action taken by General Tsao from the Liaodong military district.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.25,CG ON,TV,0000,0000,0000,,They hoped that we would follow the Spain Convention and exchange captives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.05,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kururugi Suzaku, have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.97,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.48,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.36,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.36,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.96,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:57.49,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about ideal countries, justice, or other such complicated things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:00.46,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.63,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The smile of the person I love deeply now, and the smile of the person I loved deeply in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.93,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Can you... help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.77,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.68,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Although I've eliminated Sawasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.27,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry and get my next operation going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.27,0:23:53.04,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I need to first create a place for Nunnally to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:56.91,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, I need to create a country that can control the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.91,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The plans for destruction are proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:00.75,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:04.53,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Schneiser and Cornelia... both of them together!
